{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260421162320","title":"AI-native Software Engineering membutuhkan fondasi Modern SE agar tidak mempercepat chaos","desc":"AI-native hanya efektif jika dibangun di atas modern engineering yang sudah punya pipeline, test, observability, dan boundary yang jelas.","tags":["ai-native","modern-software-engineering","readiness"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260421162320","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"aa3e6d829b2575fde24ff227695fd112","updated":1776914280708,"created":1776914280708,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421162320","id":"zettel.20260421162320","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.ai-native","alias":"ai-native","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.ai-native"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421162320","id":"zettel.20260421162320","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.modern-software-engineering","alias":"modern-software-engineering","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.modern-software-engineering"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421162320","id":"zettel.20260421162320","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.readiness","alias":"readiness","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.readiness"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421162320","id":"zettel.20260421162320","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260421162253","position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":3,"offset":1572},"end":{"line":47,"column":28,"offset":1597},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260421162253"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421162320","id":"zettel.20260421162320","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260421162310","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":3,"offset":1700},"end":{"line":48,"column":28,"offset":1725},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260421162310"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260421162320","id":"zettel.20260421162320","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","position":{"start":{"line":49,"column":3,"offset":1833},"end":{"line":49,"column":39,"offset":1869},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":118,"column":3,"offset":10679},"end":{"line":118,"column":28,"offset":10704},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421162320"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.ai-native","id":"zettel.moc.ai-native","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":3,"offset":2198},"end":{"line":31,"column":28,"offset":2223},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421162320"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":3,"offset":2537},"end":{"line":41,"column":28,"offset":2562},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421162320"}],"anchors":{"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan yang dibuka","value":"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2},"klaim-utama":{"type":"header","text":"Klaim utama","value":"klaim-utama","line":22,"column":0,"depth":2},"syarat-modern-yang-mendukung-ai-native":{"type":"header","text":"Syarat modern yang mendukung AI-native","value":"syarat-modern-yang-mendukung-ai-native","line":26,"column":0,"depth":2},"kalau-fondasi-modern-lemah":{"type":"header","text":"Kalau fondasi modern lemah","value":"kalau-fondasi-modern-lemah","line":35,"column":0,"depth":2},"failure-mode-khas":{"type":"header","text":"Failure mode khas","value":"failure-mode-khas","line":42,"column":0,"depth":2},"insight-operasional":{"type":"header","text":"Insight operasional","value":"insight-operasional","line":48,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":59,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"ai-native-software-engineering-membutuhkan-fondasi-modern-se-agar-tidak-mempercepat-chaos\">AI-native Software Engineering membutuhkan fondasi Modern SE agar tidak mempercepat chaos<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#ai-native-software-engineering-membutuhkan-fondasi-modern-se-agar-tidak-mempercepat-chaos\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Apakah AI-native SE bisa efektif tanpa modern engineering yang matang?</li>\n<li>Kondisi modern apa yang jadi syarat minimum untuk AI-native?</li>\n<li>Dengan fondasi yang lemah, failure mode AI-native apa yang paling berbahaya?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"klaim-utama\">Klaim utama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#klaim-utama\"></a></h2>\n<p>AI-native Software Engineering tidak berdiri sendiri. Ia membutuhkan fondasi Modern SE yang sehat agar AI tidak mempercepat kekacauan.</p>\n<h2 id=\"syarat-modern-yang-mendukung-ai-native\">Syarat modern yang mendukung AI-native<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#syarat-modern-yang-mendukung-ai-native\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>repository dan struktur code yang rapi.</li>\n<li>test suite yang dapat dipercaya.</li>\n<li>pipeline CI/CD yang stabil.</li>\n<li>observability dan monitoring.</li>\n<li>batas domain/komponen yang jelas.</li>\n<li>dokumentasi context yang dapat diakses.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"kalau-fondasi-modern-lemah\">Kalau fondasi modern lemah<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kalau-fondasi-modern-lemah\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>AI menjadi cermin kekacauan: outputnya cepat, tapi tetap salah.</li>\n<li>Spesifikasi jadi ambiguous karena codebase tidak konsisten.</li>\n<li>Guardrail sulit dirumuskan karena boundaries kabur.</li>\n<li>Review manusia jadi lebih sulit karena perubahan kompleks dan tersebar.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"failure-mode-khas\">Failure mode khas<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#failure-mode-khas\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fast chaos: AI menghasilkan banyak perubahan yang valid secara sintaksis tetapi salah secara domain.</li>\n<li>False confidence: test lolos sebagian, lalu bug tersembunyi masuk produksi.</li>\n<li>Overtrust: tim berhenti memeriksa karena AI tampak produktif.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"insight-operasional\">Insight operasional<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#insight-operasional\"></a></h2>\n<p>AI-native SE paling layak ketika tim sudah bisa menjawab:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>apakah spec bisa ditulis jelas?</li>\n<li>apakah context bisa dieksternalisasi?</li>\n<li>apakah pipeline validasi sudah kuat?</li>\n<li>apakah review discipline masih hidup?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Jika salah satu jawaban lemah, AI-native bukan peningkatan cepat tetapi risiko percepatan kegagalan.</p>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421162253\">Classic, Modern, dan AI-native Software Engineering adalah tiga mode kerja, bukan disiplin formal</a> — Classic, Modern, dan AI-native Software Engineering adalah tiga mode kerja, bukan disiplin formal</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421162310\">AI-native Software Engineering memindahkan gravitasi kerja engineering ke orkestrasi dan verifikasi AI</a> — AI-native Software Engineering memindahkan gravitasi kerja engineering ke orkestrasi dan verifikasi AI</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-native (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">modern-software-engineering (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">readiness (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](ht